name: Take My Freedom But Don't Take My Beard
description:
Pencil on paper by Raoof Haghighi, 15 x 11 cm (4 x 6 inches). NFT comes with the original pencil drawing, hand signed by Raoof.
 
Artwork got 7,000 likes on Instagram: www.instagram.com/p/CKJPrwZrUkn/
